Sentencas: Porous electrodes of Sr-doped lanthanum manganite in a planar solid oxide fuel cell were made by the plasma spray technique.
Titulo: PLASMA SPRAYING OF POROUS-ELECTRODES FOR A PLANAR SOLID OXIDE FUEL-CELL

Sentencas: Spherical carbon particles were utilized as an effective pore former.
Titulo: PLASMA SPRAYING OF POROUS-ELECTRODES FOR A PLANAR SOLID OXIDE FUEL-CELL

Sentencas: Spraying a mixture of annealed oxide powders sized between 50 to 200-mu-m and 15 wt% solid Carbospheres resulted in a uniform coating of 40% porosity.
Titulo: PLASMA SPRAYING OF POROUS-ELECTRODES FOR A PLANAR SOLID OXIDE FUEL-CELL

Sentencas: Porous coatings were also obtained when rigid resin intermediates were sprayed followed by annealing at 1000-degrees-C in air.
Titulo: PLASMA SPRAYING OF POROUS-ELECTRODES FOR A PLANAR SOLID OXIDE FUEL-CELL
